vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for an MF-2(A) Multifamily District on property zoned an R-7.5(A) Single Family District, on the southeast corner of West Kiest Boulevard and Guadalupe Avenue with consideration for and an ordinance granting a TH-3(A) Townhouse District
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval of an MF-2(A) Multifamily District
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval of a TH-3(A) Townhouse District 
Z223-217(MP)
